title: Missouri governor indicted on felony invasion of privacy charge
text:
Missouri governor indicted on felony invasion of privacy charge Thursday, February 22, 2018 - 01:02 
Missouri Governor Eric Greitens was indicted on a felony invasion of privacy charge on Thursday stemming from a probe into an extramarital affair involving the Republican governor.
